man\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The post continued, \\\"This is not an elite athletic kit for track and field.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The post\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"an elite athletic kit\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a costume born of patriarchal forces that are no longer welcome or needed to get eyes on women's sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a costume\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"patriarchal forces\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"eyes\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sports\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes representing other countries also sounded off on the design.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2153}, {\"ngram\": \"other countries\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"the design\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Canadian hurdler and two-time Olympian Sage Watson wrote, \\\"Yeah, that's a no from me dog,\\\" and English long jumper Abigail Irozuru shared a photo of the uniforms to her Instagram story with the caption \\\"Was ANY female athlete consulted in this team kit?!?\\\"\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2215, \"end\": 2223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9999777207452859, \"rank\": 2.2170632572667885e-05, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 2245, \"end\": 2253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999998553903, \"r